Vonage.pm is created by Production Call Processing in order to make their lives easier.
The Perl module contains some very frequently used functions and credentials, namely :
	Hop2Host : from your current host, hop to the specified host, 
                   using Linus as the in between host and use the
                   given credentials.
	Cp2Host  : vonage version of scp, copy file to host, hopping through linus
	HopBackHome : Return from the hopped-to-host and close all connections

	MAILER : Results are usually mailed. Use the specfied mailer for this.
	MAIL_LIST : send the result to people in this list.

